The Premier League returns this weekend, after European football in midweek. Champions Manchester City welcome Aston Villa in Saturday’s early kick off. Sheffield United are away to West Ham and Watford host Bournemouth. The late kick off will see Burnley take on Chelsea at Turf Moor. Saturday, October 26
FT: Manchester City 3 vs Aston Villa 0
